  "texts": [
    "When a participant y asks for feedback on a recipe x, the first step consists in predicting the stars of the input recipe S y (x) using RELEXset-Predictor.",
    "Recipe Retrieval.",
    "In the next step, a candidate subset S B x of recipes with higher quality (i.e., a higher stars value) is retrieved from RELEX-sugg-set.",
    "S B x contains all the recipes with a rating withing the range [S y (x) + 0.4, S y (x) + 0.8].",
    "For example if the rating of the input recipe S y (x) = 1, S B x will contain all the recipes with a standardized rating within the range [1.4, 1.8]."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}